lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Spaniard Garbine Muguruza, a grand slam winner who has taken down world number one Serena Williams, would be judged by most standards as a serious threat to grab the U.S. Open title.

headline.print_headline: Miracle Needed to Reach Open Final, Says Muguruza
headline.main: Miracle Needed to Reach Open Final, Says Muguruza
